column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z, p.type,  s.specobjid, s.class, s.subClass, s.z as redshift,s.zErr as redshift_Err,zWarning as redshift_Warning,  s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid,  pz.z As Photo_Z, pz.zErr AS Photo_Err, FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN Photoz as pz ON pz.objID=p.objid
